# Defense-in-depth only. The v2 bundle no longer depends on this file for
# correctness -- the logo is stored as base64 TEXT (logo_0.png.b64) and
# decoded to a binary PNG at run start by build_report.py, so line-ending
# normalization can't corrupt it even if this file is missing from a clone.
# Kept in case any real binary asset (e.g. a sample PDF) is added later.
* -text
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.pdf binary
*.py text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
.gitignore text eol=lf
